16:02.355 --> 16:04.223
- I, uh, was thinking
that if amber

16:04.291 --> 16:08.260
Traded up
from her tabloid informant

16:08.328 --> 16:11.730
To a murderous, door-slamming,
wall street executive type,

16:11.798 --> 16:15.000
