- Well, nathan felt

16:55.673 --> 16:58.108
I was working
below my qualifications

16:58.175 --> 17:00.176
At waterman's insurance.

17:03.512 --> 17:05.512
- Yeah. Hey, did you see
those gift bags?

17:05.580 --> 17:07.717
They're branded
with the bank logo.

17:07.784 --> 17:09.883
- Yeah, that's from
our fashion week party.

17:09.950 --> 17:12.185
- Do you remember seeing
either one of these two people

17:12.252 --> 17:15.020
At those events?

17:15.088 --> 17:17.255
- [scoffs]
we had so many guests.

17:17.323 --> 17:19.156
- Well, she wouldn't
have been a guest.

17:19.224 --> 17:20.891
This girl here
is amber donelli.

17:20.959 --> 17:23.794
She worked
for platinum encounters.

17:23.862 --> 17:26.796
- She's a circuit girl.
You know the term?

17:26.864 --> 17:28.464
Ge
- what's this about?

17:28.531 --> 17:30.065
- This fella in the picture,

17:30.133 --> 17:33.135
He was murdered.

17:33.203 --> 17:35.770
- Huh.
Well, I've never seen him.

17:35.838 --> 17:37.438
- Mm-hmm.

17:37.506 --> 17:38.539
- Detective, my job

17:38.607 --> 17:40.174
Is attending to the needs
of our clients.

17:40.241 --> 17:43.043
I don't interact
with the models we hire.

17:43.110 --> 17:44.310
- Does anyone else
at this bank

17:44.378 --> 17:45.845
Interact
with the models you hire?

17:45.913 --> 17:47.246
- The answer is no.

17:47.314 --> 17:48.881
I really don't like
where this is going.

17:48.948 --> 17:50.315
- Mr. Novak...

17:50.383 --> 17:53.985
Uh, a bevy of ladies like this
at a fashion week party

17:54.053 --> 17:55.653
With all your cohorts--
no interaction?

17:55.721 --> 17:57.354
That goes right into
the "who you kidding" file.

17:57.422 --> 17:59.156
- I don't care
what file it goes into.

17:59.224 --> 18:01.691
I really shouldn't continue
without benefit of counsel.

18:01.759 --> 18:03.993
- Oh.

18:04.061 --> 18:05.194
W-what happened?

18:05.262 --> 18:07.796
